description: In a world where human Professions are determined by nature, there was a person who was the strongest, despite being Jobless. Fuuta, who trained harder than anyone else to achieve this and became a champion was cast out and exiled. At the end of his wandering, he was picked up by Lilac M Fangini, the first princess and ruler of a city.>
